OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRoald Dahl museum condemns 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fauthor's anti-Semitism     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Roald Dahl Museum has condemned the
OL,6, racism of the author in a new          
OL,7, statement.                             
OL,9,FIt said it "condemns all racism        
OL,10,Fdirected at any group or individual"   
OL,11,Fand that the author's racism was       
OL,12,F"undeniable".                          
OL,14,FDahl's family apologised in 2020 for   
OL,15,Fhis anti-Semitic remarks.              
OL,17,FThe museum, in Great Missenden,        
OL,18,FBuckinghamshire, said it was working on
OL,19,Fbeing "more welcoming".                
